-end thermal-to-visible face\nverification system provides strong performance on the MILAB-VTF(B) dataset.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 21 Aug 2021 17:59:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 22 Oct 2021 22:12:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 6 Nov 2022 20:02:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-08"}
